===[[Pokémon Puzzle League]]===
Lorelei appears as a member of the Puzzle League [[Elite Four]] in [[Pokémon Puzzle League]]. She also helps tutor the player at the [[Puzzle University]].

Despite being based on her {{pkmn|animated series}} appearance, she uses her name from the games, instead of the name given to her in the English [[dub]] of ''[[Pokémon the Series]]'', Prima.

